        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Nicotine Or Vaping Access Protection and Enforcement Act of 2019 or the</b> <b>NO VAPE Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill increases civil penalties for violating restrictions on the sale and distribution of tobacco products. The bill also requires retailers to check photographic identification to verify the age of all tobacco product purchasers, with no exceptions for older purchasers.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
